channel.title: How to change a teleport name
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i380.photobucket.com/albums/oo245/zamorak_album_2008/teleport.jpg[/img] ^
I want to change this teleport name. The name is "Level 64 : Teleport To Ape Atoll"
I searched everywhere. In TextHandler and ClickingMost. I found nothing about it.
How can I change the name ? If you know it, where I change it ? Do I need to create it ?
Thanks.

item.title: How to change a teleport name
item.dc:creator: @ltownerlt ltownerlt
item.description:
@ltownerlt wrote:

no it isnt i’ve found the id go to texthandler and add this: c.sendQuest("Donator teleport", 18472); c.sendQuest("Come to the donator world", 18473);
change the text in “” and your tele will change
